<div class="map_panel">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-3">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-4 col-sm-12">
          <div class="dropdown">
            <button class="btn btn-block btn-secondary dropdown-toggle" type="button" id="hhToursMenu" data-toggle="dropdown">Touren</button>
            <div class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="hhToursMenu">
              <a class="dropdown-item" href="#">
                t1</a>
              <a class="dropdown-item" href="#">
                t2</a>
              <a class="dropdown-item" href="#">
                t3</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class=" col-4 col-sm-12 ">
          <button class="btn btn-block btn-default" type="submit">
            <%=svg "plus"%>
            Tramptour</button>
        </div>
        <div class="col-4  col-sm-12 ">
          <button class="btn btn-block btn-default" type="submit">
            <%=svg "plus"%>
            Beitrag</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="hhTourPanel" class="col-sm-9">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-8 col-6">
          <h4>Tourtitel</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4 col-6">
          <div class="btn-group" role="group">
            <button class="btn btn-default" type="submit"><%= svg "edit-2" %></button>
            <button class="btn btn-default" type="submit"><%= svg "delete" %></button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12 col-sm-10">
          <div class="mapStats">
            <div class="row">

              <div class="col-sm-3 col-6 mapStatsItem">
                Start
              </div>
              <div id="start" class="col-sm-3 col-6">
                Köln
              </div>
              <div class="col-sm-3 col-6 mapStatsItem">
                Ziel
              </div>
              <div id="destination" class="col-sm-3 col-6">
                Frankfurt
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-sm-3 col-6 mapStatsItem">
                Zeit
              </div>
              <div id="duration" class="col-sm-3 col-6">
                4 h
              </div>
              <div class="col-sm-3 col-6 mapStatsItem">
                Stops
              </div>
              <div id="amountStops" class="col-sm-3 col-6">
                3
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-10 map">
          <div id="embedmap-display" style="height:100%; width:100%;max-width:100%;">
            <iframe style="height:100%;width:100%;border:0;" frameborder="0" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed/v1/directions?origin=Köln,+Deutschland&destination=Frankfurt+am+Main,+Deutschland&key=AIzaSyBFw0Qbyq9zTFTd-tUY6dZWTgaQzuU17R8"></iframe>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div id="text" class="col-sm-8">
          <p>Dies ist ein wichtiger Text übers Trampen. Trampen ist super toll. Nichts ist toller als Trampen. Es ist gesund, weil man ist viel an der frischen Luft. Sonne kriegt man auch ab. Nette Menschen lernt man kennen.</p>
        </div>
        <div id="picture" class="col-sm-4">
          pic
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
